        //统计总分by djf
        function SumZpf(col){
            //评教师table
            var objTable=document.getElementById("Datagrid1");
            //总行数
            var rowlength=objTable.rows.length;
            //总列数
            var collength=objTable.rows[0].cells.length;
            //总评分
            var intZpf=0.0;
            var currTr ,i,ddl,lbl,tempNum,lastNum;
            for (i=1;i<rowlength;i++){
                //当前行
                currTr= objTable.rows[i];
                //评分下拉框
                //alert(currTr.cells[col-1].innerText);
                ddl=currTr.cells[col-1].firstChild;
                lbl=currTr.cells[col-1].getElementsByTagName("span")[0];
                if (ddl.options[ddl.selectedIndex].value!='') {tempNum= parseFloat('0'+ddl.options[ddl.selectedIndex].value)*parseFloat('0'+currTr.cells[collength-1].innerText);lbl.innerText=Math.round(tempNum*1000)/1000;}
                else {tempNum=0.0;lbl.innerText="";}
                //计算总评分
                intZpf=intZpf + tempNum;
                if ((i==rowlength-1) && (tempNum!=0.0)){lastNum=Math.round(tempNum*1000)/1000}　else {lastNum=""}

            }
            objTable.rows[rowlength-1].cells[col-1].getElementsByTagName("span")[0].innerText=lastNum+"  总分：" + Math.round(intZpf*1000)/1000;
        }

        function NumCheck(obj){
            var reg1=/^(([1-9]\d*)|0)(\.\d{1,2})?$/;
            var str = obj.value;

            var r1 = str.match(reg1);
            if (str!="")
            {
                if(r1 == null||parseFloat(str)>100)
                {
                    alert("总体印象分必须为小于等于100的数字,且小数点位数不能超过2位！")
                    obj.value="";
                    obj.focus();
                    return false;
                }
            }
            return true;
        }
        function Hide(){
            document.getElementById("Popup").style.display="none";
        }
        function show(evt,str_xx){
            xm=str_xx;
            if(navigator.appName.indexOf("Explorer")>-1){
                document.getElementById("td1").innerText="" + xm;
            }else{
                document.getElementById("td1").textContent="" + xm;
            }
            //document.getElementById("td2").innerText="" + str_jxb;
            evt=evt?evt:(window.event?window.event:null);
            x=evt.clientX + "px";
            y=evt.clientY + "px";
            document.getElementById("Popup").style.display="block";
            document.getElementById("Popup").style.left = x;
            document.getElementById("Popup").style.top = y;
        }

<script language="javascript">

    var $;
    if (document.getElementById) {
        $ = function() {
            var elements = new Array();
            for (var i = 0; i < arguments.length; i++) {
                var element = arguments[i];
                if (typeof element == 'string') {
                    element = document.getElementById(element);
                }
                if (arguments.length == 1) {
                    return element;
                }
                elements.push(element);
            }
            return elements;
        };
    }
    else if (document.all) {
        $ = function() {
            var elements = new Array();
            for (var i = 0; i < arguments.length; i++) {
                var element = arguments[i];
                if (typeof element == 'string') {
                    element = document.all[element];
                }
                if (arguments.length == 1) {
                    return element;
                }
                elements.push(element);
            }
            return elements;
        };
    }
